@startuml Sequência Detalhada - Bloqueio Automático

!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam shadowing false

title Sequência Detalhada - Sistema de Detecção e Bloqueio Automático

actor "Zeek Monitor\n(Background)" as Monitor #LightBlue
participant "ZeekService" as Zeek #LightGreen
participant "IncidentService" as Incident #LightYellow
participant "AliasService" as Alias #LightCoral
participant "pfSense API" as PfAPI #Orange
participant "MySQL DB" as DB #LightGray
participant "pfSense\nFirewall" as Firewall #LightPink

== [1] Monitoramento e Detecção ==

Monitor -> Zeek: GET /api/scanners/zeek/logs\nlogfile=notice.log
activate Zeek

Zeek -> PfAPI: GET /zeek-api/alert_data.php
activate PfAPI
PfAPI --> Zeek: JSON com logs
deactivate PfAPI

Zeek -> Zeek: Analisa logs\nDetecta SQL Injection
Zeek -> Zeek: Cria ZeekIncident

note right of Zeek
  <b>⏱️ 2.281s</b>
  💻 CPU: 6.80%
  🧠 RAM: 35.79 MB
end note

Zeek --> Monitor: Incidentes detectados
deactivate Zeek

== [2] Salvamento do Incidente ==

Monitor -> Incident: POST /api/incidents/\n{device_ip, incident_type, ...}
activate Incident

Incident -> DB: INSERT INTO zeek_incidents
activate DB
DB --> Incident: ID criado
deactivate DB

Incident -> Incident: Verifica "Atacante" no tipo
Incident -> Incident: Thread Background.start()

note right of Incident
  <b>⏱️ 2.499s</b>
  💻 CPU: 13.70%
  🧠 RAM: 35.79 MB
end note

Incident --> Monitor: Incidente salvo (ID)
deactivate Incident

== [3] Processamento em Background ==

Monitor -> Monitor: Thread aguarda 0.5s

Monitor -> Incident: POST /api/incidents/process-batch\n?limit=10
activate Incident

Incident -> DB: SELECT * FROM zeek_incidents\nWHERE processed_at IS NULL
activate DB
DB --> Incident: Lista de incidentes
deactivate DB

loop Para cada incidente "Atacante"
    Incident -> DB: UPDATE zeek_incidents\nSET processed_at = NOW()
    activate DB
    DB --> Incident: OK
    deactivate DB
    
    Incident -> Incident: _apply_auto_block(incident)
    activate Incident
end

note right of Incident
  <b>⏱️ 3.222s</b>
  💻 CPU: 16.10%
  🧠 RAM: 35.79 MB
end note

Incident --> Monitor: Processamento concluído
deactivate Incident

== [4] Verificação de Alias ==

Incident -> Alias: get_alias_by_name("Bloqueados")
activate Alias

Alias -> DB: SELECT * FROM pfsense_aliases\nWHERE name = 'Bloqueados'
activate DB
DB --> Alias: Dados do alias
deactivate DB

Alias -> PfAPI: GET /api/v2/firewall/alias\n(Verifica no pfSense)
activate PfAPI
PfAPI --> Alias: Dados do pfSense
deactivate PfAPI

note right of Alias
  <b>⏱️ 2.245s</b>
  💻 CPU: 16.70%
  🧠 RAM: 35.79 MB
end note

Alias --> Incident: Alias encontrado
deactivate Alias

== [5] Adição de IP ao Alias ==

Incident -> Alias: add_addresses_to_alias\n("Bloqueados", [{address: IP}])
activate Alias

Alias -> DB: INSERT INTO pfsense_alias_addresses\n(alias_id, address, detail)
activate DB
DB --> Alias: Endereço inserido
deactivate DB

Alias -> PfAPI: PUT /api/v2/firewall/alias/{id}\n{address: [...IPs...]}
activate PfAPI
PfAPI -> PfAPI: Atualiza configuração
PfAPI --> Alias: Alias atualizado
deactivate PfAPI

note right of Alias
  <b>⏱️ 2.233s</b>
  💻 CPU: 25.00%
  🧠 RAM: 35.85 MB
end note

Alias --> Incident: IP adicionado
deactivate Alias

== [6] Aplicação no Firewall ==

Incident -> PfAPI: POST /api/v2/firewall/apply
activate PfAPI

PfAPI -> Firewall: Valida configurações
activate Firewall
Firewall -> Firewall: Reconstrói tabelas
Firewall -> Firewall: Aplica regras
Firewall -> Firewall: Encerra conexões do IP
Firewall --> PfAPI: Mudanças aplicadas
deactivate Firewall

note right of PfAPI
  <b>⏱️ 2.326s</b>
  💻 CPU: 38.90%
  🧠 RAM: 35.85 MB
  <b>🔥 Maior carga!</b>
end note

PfAPI --> Incident: Aplicado com sucesso
deactivate PfAPI

== [7] Finalização ==

Incident -> DB: UPDATE zeek_incidents\nSET status = 'resolved'
activate DB
DB --> Incident: Status atualizado
deactivate DB

Incident -> DB: INSERT INTO blocking_feedback_history\n(admin_reason, ...)
activate DB
DB --> Incident: Feedback criado
deactivate DB

Incident --> Monitor: ✅ Bloqueio completo

note over Monitor, Firewall
  <b>📊 RESUMO</b>
  
  <b>⏱️ Tempo Total: ~14.8 segundos</b>
  
  <b>Distribuição:</b>
  1. get_logs: 2.281s (15.4%)
  2. save_incident: 2.499s (16.9%)
  3. process_incidents: 3.222s (21.8%) ← Mais lento
  4. get_alias: 2.245s (15.2%)
  5. add_addresses: 2.233s (15.1%)
  6. apply_firewall: 2.326s (15.7%)
  
  <b>💻 CPU:</b>
  - Média: ~19.7%
  - Máximo: 38.90% (apply_firewall)
  
  <b>🧠 RAM:</b>
  - Estável: 35.79-35.85 MB
  - Sem vazamento
end note

@enduml

